replies.body:
{{champion:122}} is so god damn fun to play, even though I know my fun is at the total expense of my opponent's fun, dammit it's enjoyable to hook btches, dunk fools, and spin2win.

{{champion:157}} {{champion:412}} I don't play them but I can see how they can be fun. Their kits flow nicely and they have some neat and visually pleasing interactions.

But I can never, ever, ever forgive the creation of {{champion:429}}
